summary: Makes the Orcish man bun playable and fully compatible with elves! Finally!
descriptionHtml:
Have you ever wanted your elven character to have a man bun? Now you can!
<br />
<br />I made this a long while ago but decided to be selfish and kept it to myself. Not anymore. This is for the small crowd of people who want man buns but aren't Orcs.
author: there should really be a name change option
